# SPDX-License-Identifier: Apache-2.0

# The signaling image only needs generated Go bindings and its own source.
# Keep credentials, repository metadata, and local build products out of the
# Docker build context, including when a remote builder is configured.
**
!gen/
!gen/go/
!gen/go/**
!services/
!services/signaling/
!services/signaling/**

# Defense in depth if a sensitive file is ever created in an allowed tree.
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/secrets/
**/secrets/**
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/*.p8
**/*.p12
**/*.pfx
**/*.mobileprovision
**/id_rsa*
**/id_ed25519*
**/.git/
**/.git/**
**/bin/
**/bin/**
**/coverage.out
**/*.log
